────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Honest summary (post 2026-05-24 strategic decision)
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

DARIO is a prompt library + helper scripts for Claude Code, operated as
a consulting accelerator under Automation Solution AI. The value lives
in:

  - Curation: 580+ skills organised across 32 squads
  - Workflow design: Padrão A polished wrappers, dispatch patterns,
    pre-flight validators, telemetry layer
  - Operator know-how: barda's hands-on engagement with each client

The value does NOT live in obfuscated binaries or cryptographic anti-
piracy measures. Those were removed 2026-05-24 (see
orchestrator/RFC_STRATEGIC_DECISIONS.md) because they defended against
zero real threats. A determined attacker bypasses any obfuscation in
30 minutes; the cost/benefit was negative.

────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
What you can do
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

1. EVALUATION (7-day trial, no key required)
   - Install on one machine for evaluation
   - Read source code to understand behavior
   - Run all skills, scripts, tests
   - Automatic expiry after 7 days unless activated

2. WITH A VALID LICENSE KEY (purchased via barda@automationsolutionai.com)
   - Use indefinitely (PRO = R$ 297/month) or higher tier
   - Apply to your own client work
   - Receive updates + barda's support during paid period

3. AUTOMATION SOLUTION AI ENGAGEMENT (consulting model)
   - Per-engagement contract terms (not covered by this LICENSE alone)
   - DARIO installed at your company, barda operates with you
   - Pricing tied to results, not tool usage

